item.title: Fashion Passion
item.description:
We’ve seen Toy Story where toys come to life, we’ve seen inside out where emotions come to life, but now in Fashion Passion, CLOTHES come to life!

What will these mischievous garments get up to in Fashion Passion!

Story Quest is a wild ride of wicked tales and wacky stories, all suggested by none other than the masterminds themselves, THE KIDS!
